python3 -m venv venv (To create virtaul env)
source ./venv/bin/activate (To activate virtual env)

pip install Flask prometheus_client psutil (To instal dependencies)

brew services start prometheus
brew services start grafana 

to start the server of local host bash command in main.py directory:-
uvicorn main:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000

to start local host and give post req
curl -X POST "http://localhost:8000/predict" -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"input": 7}'

--------------------------------------------




For new linear regression model

curl -X POST http://localhost:5000/predict -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"features": [8.1, 3.5, 3.0, 0.2]}'

now app_request_total and app_inference_time_seconds is visible in prometheus

Check metrics at http://localhost:5000/metrics
Check Prometheus UI at http://localhost:9090
Check Grafana  http://localhost:3000    admin admin 

